# API backend credentials — OPTIONAL. The default backend ("cli") uses a
# local agent CLI's own authentication (Claude Code subscription OAuth /
# Gemini CLI / Codex CLI / etc.) and needs no environment variables here.
#
# Set the variables below ONLY if you want to run the API backend
# (`--backend api`) against DeepSeek or another OpenAI-compatible endpoint.

# PAPER_DIGEST_LLM_API_KEY=sk-xxx
# PAPER_DIGEST_LLM_BASE_URL=https://api.deepseek.com/v1
